    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Northern Pacific railroad\nhas served notice on the county\ncommissioners that no more char\nity rates will be given by that line\nwhere the fare is under IS cents.\nThis. means that the cost of send\ning a patient to the county poor\nfarm at Spangle will now be\ndoubled. Heretofore, under the\ncharity rate, the fare to Spangle\nfor the 1nfortunates sent there by\nthe county over the Northern Pa\ncific has been 30 cents, but under\nthe new ruling the county must\npay the regular fare, 80 cents."
    }
